Collections.rule:
Individual: @CH* (mm:uuidEncode)
	Types: PointsStats
	Facts: isStatsOf @Q*,
		AvgPoints @CH* (xsd:double),
		AvgFieldGoal2Made @CI* (xsd:double),
		AvgFieldGoal2Percent @CJ* (xsd:double),
		AvgFieldGoal3Made @CK* (xsd:double),
		AvgFieldGoal3Percent @CM* (xsd:double),
		AvgFreeThrowMade @CU* (xsd:double),
		AvgFreeThrowPercent @CW* (xsd:double),
		AvgPointsAgainst @DP* (xsd:double)

Individual: @AP* (mm:uuidEncode)
	Types: TechnicalStats
	Facts: isStatsOf @Q* (mm:uuidEncode),
		Rebounds @AP* (xsd:integer),
		Assists @AR* (xsd:integer),
		Turnovers @AV* (xsd:integer),
		FoulsCommitted @BF* (xsd:integer),
		FoulsDrawn @BN* (xsd:integer), 
		Win @CC*(xsd:integer)

Individual: @R* (mm:uuidEncode)
	Types: PointsStats
	Facts: isStatsOf @Q* (mm:uuidEncode),
		Points @AT* (xsd:integer),
		FieldGoal2Made @T* (xsd:integer),
		FieldGoal2Percent @V* (xsd:double),
		FieldGoal3Made @Y* (xsd:integer),
		FieldGoal3Percent @AA* (xsd:double),
		FreeThrowMade @AI* (xsd:integer),
		FreeThrowPercent @AK* (xsd:double),
		PointsAgainst @BD* (xsd:integer)

Individual: @Q*
	Types: Team
	Facts: TeamCity @P*,
		TeamName @Q*,
		playedAs @Q* (mm:uuidEncode),
		hasStats @CH* (mm:uuidEncode),
		hasStats@DB* (mm:uuidEncode),
		TeamAbbr @O*

Individual: @R* (mm:uuidEncode)
	Types: Stats
	Facts: isStatsOf @Q* (mm:uuidEncode),
		Points @AT* (xsd:integer),
		FieldGoal2Made @T* (xsd:integer),
		FieldGoal2Percent @V* (xsd:decimal),
		FieldGoal3Made @Y* (xsd:integer),
		FieldGoal3Percent @AA* (xsd:decimal),
		FreeThrowMade @AI* (xsd:integer),
		FreeThrowPercent @AK* (xsd:decimal),
		Rebounds @AP* (xsd:integer),
		Assists @AR* (xsd:integer),
		Turnovers @AV* (xsd:integer),
		PointsAgainst @BD* (xsd:integer),
		FoulsCommitted @BF* (xsd:integer),
		FoulsDrawn @BN* (xsd:integer), 
		Win @CC*

Individual: @DB* (mm:uuidEncode)
	Types: TechnicalStats
	Facts: isStatsOf @Q* ,
		AvgRebounds @DB* (xsd:double),
		AvgAssists @DD* (xsd:double),
		AvgTurnovers @DH* (xsd:double),
		AvgFoulsCommitted @DR* (xsd:double),
		AvgFoulsDrawn @DZ* (xsd:double), 
		AvgWin @EO* (xsd:double)

Individual: @Q* (mm:uuidEncode)
	Types: GameTeam
	Facts: isTeam @Q*,
	          isGameTeamOf @B*,
	          hasStats @R* (mm:uuidEncode),
	          hasStats @AP* (mm:uuidEncode)

Individual: @B*
	Types: Game
	Facts: GameLocation @M*,
	          HomeTeam @L*,
	          AwayTeam @H*,
	          hasGameTeam @Q* (mm:uuidEncode)
